【Hollow-out Drawer & Metal Slide Rail】This bathroom cabinet drawer has no handle design to reduce the risk of collision, and it can also make the cabinet look tidy and comfortable. Smooth metal slides keep the drawer running smoothly and are easy to use.

【Worry-Free After-sales】The numbered parts and detailed instructions carried by the slim bathroom cabinet ensure that you can easily complete the assembly in your spare afternoon. If you encounter problems, please feel free to contact us for help.
